      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那添加事件的时候，SchedulerApp是直接创建Event对象，还是需要经过什么中间层？另外事件数据最终存到哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "SchedulerApp直接new一个Event，构造函数里传入Logistics_Warehouse作为关联。然后Event自己要调用EventDAO的add_event方法，这里传入的是物流配送路线Logistics_DeliveryRoute。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "Logistics_Warehouse",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute",
        "add_event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把添加事件的流程画出来了：User请求到SchedulerApp，SA创建Event（带仓储参数），然后EV调用EVDAO的add_event（带配送路线参数），最后返回确认。接下来是提醒功能吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "SchedulerApp",
        "Event",
        "EventDAO",
        "add_event"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
