      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，用户还要能设置提醒。这个流程类似，但走Reminder和ReminderService。提醒需要关联车队管理Logistics_FleetManagement，调度时还要检查库存水平Logistics_StockLevel。",
